          sat_inv s' hj' \<Gamma> \<and> h' = FractionalHeap.normalize (get_fh H') \<and> Some H' = Some h'' \<oplus> Some hj' \<oplus> Some hf1 \<and> safe n (Some \<Gamma>) C' (s', h'') (add_states S ?R)"
